This paper deals with the design of an optimal online policy for minimizing the Age of Information (AoI) at the destination, subject to energy causality constraints at the sensor. The problem involves a noisy channel, and the absence of channel state information or transmission feedback at the sensor. These characteristics suggest that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Networked Systems (cs.NI), Machine Learning (cs.MA), and Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
